cu.explanation_en: Setting the second integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the CSI-RS enable flag to a negative value will cause configuration validation failure and prevent the DU from initializing properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 CSI-RS 啟用標誌設定為負值，會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止 DU 正確初始化。
